{
  "texts": [
    "proposed a blockchain-based medical data preservation scheme for telecare medical information systems.",
    "In their study, medical data were stored on the blockchain for access only by authorized parties.",
    "Additionally, ECC-based Diffie-Hellman key exchange was used for sensors and mobile devices to negotiate the common session key [10].Liu et al.",
    "designed a medical data sharing and protection scheme based on a hospital's private blockchain.",
    "The scheme had a symptoms-matching mechanism that allowed two patients with the same symptoms to communicate about their illness."
  ]
}